{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "7cc7cc25-4ef7-467a-9766-09fc4b085a8d",
    "name": "Course Marketplace Backend API",
    "description": "Importable Postman Collection for the Course Marketplace Backend.\n\nThis collection is organized by backend module and kept in sync with the currently mounted routes.\n\nResponse envelope:\n- success: boolean\n- message: string\n- data: object | array | null\n- meta: optional pagination metadata\n\nCurrent auth flow:\n- Signup and email verification: /api/v1/auth/*\n- Protected business-route session auth: Better Auth under /api/auth/*\n- Legacy compatibility login routes still exist under /api/v1/auth/*, but protected course-platform APIs depend on the Better Auth session used by authorize() middleware\n\nImplemented modules in this version:\n- Health\n- Auth\n- Users\n- Course Categories\n- Courses\n\nPlanned future modules to append into this same collection:\n- Lessons\n- Enrollments\n- Payments\n- Reviews\n- Admin",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
